full_title: Girl, so confusing by Charli xcx
title: Girl, so confusing

description.plain:
“Girl, so confusing” is the tenth track on Charli XCX’s sixth studio album, BRAT, releasing on June 7, 2024.

On April 2, 2024, Charli announced the song and confirmed that it would appear on BRAT via a voice memo sent to a small number of fans.
